The Choco-Story Experience

   1

DISCOVER

the history of chocolate

   Dive into the wonderful world of chocolate for a incredible travel
   through the ages !

   1

TASTE

all you can eat !

   Choco-expert who can describe hidden flavours of origin chocolates? Or
   just chocolate lover to try all the chocolates ?

   1

MEET

our chocolatiers

   Live demonstration every day, all day long, just for pleasure. Kids and
   adults are most welcome !

   1

CREATE

your own chocolates

   Join one of our worshops for kids or adults to make your chocolates!
   Reveal the choco-power in you!

   >>>

   >>>

   >>>

   >>>

   1

FUN

for the whole family

   A playful tour for kids is available to have little brothers and
   sisters to discover the world of chocolate… with FUN !

   1

SEE

art with chocolate

   3m height, 200kg chocolate for a more realistic sculpture than the
   building itself! Discover the area dedicated to whatever you could
   imagine with chocolate !

   1

MEET

the most famous fans

   Who are the famous chocolate-lover celebrities? Find out who left their
   mark in our Wall of Fame!

   1

AND FOR YOU

What will be the next chocolate experience?

   If you think you saw everything about chocolate, there is still some
   experiences to create!

   >>>

   >>>

   >>>

   >>>

